duties_responsibilities.duty: Assist in creating interior design concepts and plans for client projects.
Collaborate with senior designers to select materials, furniture, and decor that meet client needs and budgets.
Assist in creating 3D renderings and visualizations of interior spaces using design software.
Coordinate with vendors, contractors, and suppliers to ensure timely delivery and installation of design elements.

education_certification.credential: Currently studying Interior Design OR 1 year of experience in the field
